text: Sabeeh Abed Ali (), is a coach and former international Iraqi football player, who played for Iraq in the 1972 AFC Asian Cup qualification and 1974 FIFA World Cup qualification, he also played for Al-Minaa.History of Iraqi Sports, 1971 (in Arabic) ==Honours== ===Local=== ;Al-Mina'a * 1978 Iraqi League: Champion ===International=== ;Iraq * 1972 World Military Championships: Champion ==References== ==External links== * Iraqi national team players database *Al-Minaa Club: Sailors of south Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Al-Mina'a SC players Category:Sportspeople from Basra Category:Iraq international footballers Category:Association football fullbacks Category:Iraqi football managers Category:Al-Mina'a SC managers Category:Year of birth missing Category:1980s deaths
